Policies are attached to a Role.

eg of a policy: AmzonS3FullAccess; AmazonS3ReadOnlyAccess

AWS EC2 instance Metadata:
  it allows ec2 instances to learn about themselves WITHOUT USING AN IAM ROLE.
  https://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data
  You can retrieve the IAM role name from the metadata, but CANNOT retrieve the IAM policy.
  used with a curl command.
  
AWS SDK:
  If you dont specify or configure a default region, then us-east-1 will be chosen by default.
  used to code against AWS services.
  
  
  
